<section class="cta-final">
  <div class="reveal">
    <span class="sec-label">Prêt à voir la vérité ?</span>
    <h2>Rejoins les premiers <em>early adopters</em></h2>
    <p>Sois parmi les premiers à tester MyTradingCoach. Ton feedback construit directement le produit.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register" class="btn-p" style="font-size:15px;padding:14px 30px">
        Commencer gratuitement →
      </a>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--txt3)">Pas de CB · Pas d'engagement · Données en France 🇫🇷 · Indépendant & bootstrappé</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-final {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 5%;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-final::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    width: 500px; height: 250px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(59,130,246,.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-final h2 { max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 18px; }
  .cta-final p { color: var(--txt2); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 300; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 44px; }

  .btn-p {
    background: var(--blue);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    border-radius: 9px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(59,130,246,.4);
    transition: all .2s;
    font-family: var(--disp);
  }

  .btn-p:hover { background: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 0 44px rgba(59,130,246,.55); }
</style>
